  <title>Basics</title>

  <p>
    To play <app>Hexkudo</app>, start by selecting a difficulty level and a puzzle shape.
    You can play <app>Hexkudo</app> with the keyboard, the mouse, or a combination of the two.
  </p>

  <section id="select">
    <title>Choosing a Puzzle</title>

    <p>To start a game, the first step consists of selecting a difficulty level between Easy, Medium, and Hard.</p>
    <p>
      The next step consists of selecting a puzzle shape.
      With the Random option, <app>Hexkudo</app> randomly selects a shape for you.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section id="keyboard-mouse">
    <title>Using the Keyboard and the Mouse</title>

    <p>You can use the keyboard to play <app>Hexkudo</app>:</p>

    <list>
      <item><p>Select a cell by using the arrow or the <key>Tab</key> keys.</p></item>
      <item><p>To enter a number, select the cell and type the number.</p></item>
      <item><p>To remove a number, select the cell and press <key>Delete</key>.</p></item>
    </list>

    <p>You can also use the mouse:</p>

    <list>
      <item><p>Select a cell by clicking it with the mouse.</p></item>
      <item>
        <p>
          Click the number to add to the cell.
          Numbers that you already entered are displayed in blue in the number picker.
        </p>
        <media type="image" src="figures/select-number.png">
          <p>Selecting a number</p>
        </media>
      </item>
      <item><p>To remove a number, click the cell and click <gui style="button">Clear</gui>.</p></item>
    </list>

    <p>You can also draw the path with the mouse:</p>
    <list>
      <item><p>Click a cell that already has a number and hold the mouse button.</p></item>
      <item><p>Drag the mouse to an adjacent cell: this new cell gets the next number.</p></item>
      <item><p>Continue dragging the mouse along the path to complete the puzzle.</p></item>
    </list>

    <p>You can perform this drag motion with the left button to draw the path in the ascending number order.</p>
    <media type="image" src="figures/drag-up.png">
      <p>Drawing the path with the left mouse button</p>
    </media>

    <p>Use the right button to draw the path in the descending number order.</p>
    <media type="image" src="figures/drag-down.png">
      <p>Drawing the path with the right mouse button</p>
    </media>
  </section>
